last_episode_to_air.name: Reaching Home Plate
last_episode_to_air.overview: Na-eun and Jun-hyeong work through their nerves in their own ways before the wedding. Choi Hui-seon sees Jang Min-woo in a new light.

name: Welcome to Wedding Hell
overview: A marriage proposal is supposed to be a happy ending. But for one couple, it becomes the beginning of an uphill struggle over wedding preparations.

episodes.name: First Pitch
episodes.overview: Doubt and frustration bubble up for Kim Na-eun as her boyfriend Seo Jun-hyeong deflects every time she wants to talk about marriage.

episodes.name: Missed Sign
episodes.overview: The first step is also one of the most important: having their parents meet. Na-eun and Jun-hyeong nervously hope for a smooth evening.

episodes.name: Drag Bunt
episodes.overview: Na-eun frets over how to broach the topic of finances with Jun-hyeong, who seems to have her opposite philosophy when it comes to spending.

episodes.name: Outfield Fly Ball
episodes.overview: A peek at Jun-hyeong's credit card statement horrifies Na-eun. She has no idea that he's planning an extravagant bridal shower behind her back.

episodes.name: Relief Pitcher
episodes.overview: A battle of wills unfolds as Jun-hyeong pushes to book an expensive wedding venue at a hotel, while Na-eun prefers something more reasonable.

episodes.name: Beanball
episodes.overview: An array of impressive gifts from Jun-hyeong's mother delights Na-eun and her parents — until they see the hefty price tag left attached.

episodes.name: Error
episodes.overview: Na-eun's search for a sought-after luxury watch for Jun-hyeong proves challenging. When he calls one day with surprising news, her mood sours.

episodes.name: Ground into Double Play
episodes.overview: When Jun-hyeong's mother offers to help pick out furniture, Na-eun cannot decline. A day out shopping falls by the wayside.

episodes.name: Bench-Clearing Brawl
episodes.overview: A fierce disagreement between the two mothers over the couple's new home places Na-eun and Jun-hyeong in the hot seat.

episodes.name: Suspended Game
episodes.overview: The wedding photo shoot approaches, but Na-eun and Jun-hyeong are not on speaking terms. Their friends set out to help them make up.

episodes.name: Home Run
episodes.overview: While the fate of the wedding hangs in the balance, the mothers finally sit down for a heart-to-heart. Jun-hyeong comes to an important realization.

episodes.name: Reaching Home Plate
episodes.overview: Na-eun and Jun-hyeong work through their nerves in their own ways before the wedding. Choi Hui-seon sees Jang Min-woo in a new light.
